{"tid":934264,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"白安<讓我逃離平庸的生活> 聽左未?","createTime":"2018-12-09T06:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T13:13:33.000Z","uid":117977,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbb2069d9864559d7b07042fb95d4f0c4d3f37a","tid":934264,"uid":117977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jgx-q0jYxwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Djgx-q0jYxwg&d=PSRvB71USbKvCiCuTlXTSTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=39d9fb77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jgx-q0jYxwg</a><br />\n只要還擁有自己，就不是一無所有<br />\n<br />\n白安:「這首歌不只是我逃離我的平庸生活，每個人都有屬於自己最獨特的生活，希望大家聽到這首歌時也會有勇氣找到自己、更接近自己，沒有人是平庸的，每個人都有屬於自己的天空。」<br />\n<br />\n因為當初&lt;是什麼讓我遇見這樣的你&gt;而認識了白安, 當年還在讀書,現在開始工作,突如而來的&lt;讓凡逃離平庸的生活&gt;讓我揪著心,好想回到自己想要的生活。<br />\n<br />\n《讓我逃離平庸的生活》寫的除了是白安這四年來糾結的心境，同時也為90年代出生的年輕人發聲，白安希望藉由這首充滿力量正面能量的歌，鼓勵這個世代年輕人，用力去追、奮力去闖，勇敢擁抱曾經痛恨的傷口，讓未來只屬於自己，成功逃離那重複無味的平庸。<br />\n<br />\n新碟''1990s'' 14/12 面世,  我會支持! 各位巴絲打呢? 有無人鐘意白安 獨特的唱腔?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b651a3d73097a74dcb1459db1a07f9aa087b0115","tid":934264,"uid":117977,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aVmZpcrQBU4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaVmZpcrQBU4&d=PSRvB71USbKvCiCuTlXTSTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7707acae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aVmZpcrQBU4</a><br />\n2018仍然有聽既舉手"},{"pid":"2977dbc8f2af95aa5f6217c4d834e65909212e16","tid":934264,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:56:43.000Z","msg":"佢呢4年究竟去左邊??"},{"pid":"ea5b5e4239d399a0eb2d0f6a6ca2fdb0e4009112","tid":934264,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"好低產"},{"pid":"34fc5ec09ecce0c4b9ed0fcbf9b443